text: Yasabhanda badhi atyacariko hola jasale allahabare asatyakura gardacha. Yasta manisaharu allahako samu prastuta garinechan ra sabai saksiharule bhannechan ki yinai manisa hun jasale aphno palanakartabare jhutha kura bhaneka thi'e, khabaradara (savadhana) atyacariharumathi allahako dhikkara cha
